## Diagram 4: Risk Assessment Engine

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    AssessConnectionRisk()                        │
│                                                                 │
│  Input: []Connection, map[int]Info, *Config                     │
│                                                                 │
│  Pre-computation:                                              │
│  ├─ procCount[process] = count of outbound connections         │
│  └─ ipCount[remoteAddr] = count of outbound connections         │
│                                                                 │
│  For each outbound connection:                                  │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ count = 0                                               │    │
│  │ isWhitelisted = cfg.IsWhitelistedIP(remoteAddr)         │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if !isWhitelisted && IsSuspiciousPort(remotePort):      │    │
│  │     reasons[count] = "suspicious port XXXX"             │    │
│  │     count++                                             │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if !isWhitelisted && IsSuspiciousProcess(process):      │    │
│  │     reasons[count] = "suspicious process: XXX"          │    │
│  │     count++                                             │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if IsTransitionState(state):                            │    │
│  │     reasons[count] = "connection state: XXX"            │    │
│  │     count++                                             │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if ipCount[remoteAddr] >= cfg.Thresholds.MinIP:         │    │
│  │     reasons[count] = "high connection count to X.X.X.X" │    │
│  │     count++                                             │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if procCount[process] >= cfg.Thresholds.MinProcess:     │    │
│  │     reasons[count] = "high outbound count for XXX"      │    │
│  │     count++                                             │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ if info, ok := secInfo[PID]; ok:                        │    │
│  │     if privEscReason(info) != "":                       │    │
│  │         reasons[count] = "PRIV ESCALATION: ..."         │    │
│  │         count++                                         │    │
│  │                                                         │    │
│  │ Assign risk level:                                     │    │
│  │   count >= critical_threshold → critical               │    │
│  │   count >= high_threshold     → high                   │    │
│  │   count == 1                → medium                   │    │
│  │   count == 0                → skip (no risk)           │    │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                                                 │
│  Output: []ConnectionRisk                                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              AssessConnectionRiskWithThreatIntel()              │
│                                                                 │
│  Input: []ConnectionRisk, *ThreatIntelDB                        │
│                                                                 │
│  For each risk:                                                │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ match := tiDB.LookupConnection(remoteAddr)              │    │
│  │ if match != nil:                                        │    │
│  │     for each ioc in match.IOCs:                         │    │
│  │         reasons += "THREAT_INTEL: family (source)       │    │
│  │                       confidence=X country=XX"          │    │
│  │         if ioc.Confidence >= 90:                        │    │
│  │             riskLevel = critical                        │    │
│  │         elif ioc.Confidence >= 80:                      │    │
│  │             if riskLevel in (low, medium):              │    │
│  │                 riskLevel = high                        │    │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                                                 │
│  Output: []ConnectionRisk (enriched with threat intel)          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

